<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA57">
<l>vaḻittaṅku valviṉaiyai māṟṟāṉō neñcē</l>
<l>taḻīikkoṇṭu pōravuṇaṉ ṟaṉṉai cuḻitteṅkun</l>
<l>tāḻviṭaṅkaḷ paṟṟip pulālveḷḷan tāṉukaḷa</l>
<l>vāḻvaṭaṅka mārviṭanta māl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will he not change the harsh deeds established on the way, heart?</l>
<l>– Māl who took the war Asura in an embrace [and], bending [and] seizing</l>
<l>lowered sides everywhere so that a flood of [his] flesh lept up,</l>
<l>dug up the chest, so that the life was subdued.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
